Title: Anna Karenina
Writer: Vasily Katanyan, Leo Tolstoy (novel), Aleksandr Zarkhi
Actors: Tatyana Samoylova, Nikolai Gritsenko, Vasiliy Lanovoy, Yuriy Yakovlev
Plot: Anna Karenina is a young wife of an older husband. She has an affair with the handsome Count Vronsky. By following her desires Anna complicates her life.
